five dollars; for such a vehicle which is more than ten model years old, fifty-five dollars; for such a vehicle which is more than thirteen model years old, forty-five dollars; and for such a vehicle which is more than fifteen model years old, thirty-five dollars.}}}\par}{}{\pard\plain\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri0\li0{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{(2)}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{For a combined gross weight exceeding three tons but not exceeding nine tons, the annual registration fee shall be as set forth in the following schedule:}}}\par}{\pard\plain\keep\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\sb80\ri1084\li1084{For a combined}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~}}}{And not}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{The annual}\par}{\pard\plain\keep\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keep\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{ gross weight}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~}}}{exceeding:}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{registration}\par}{\pard\plain\keep\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keep\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{ exceeding:}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~\~}}}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{fee shall be:}\par}{\pard\plain\keep\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keep\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{3 Tons}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{4 Tons}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{$}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{80}\par}{\pard\plain\keep\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084\sa0\par}{\pard\plain\keep\keepn\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj\fi0\ri1084\li1084{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{4 Tons}{{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj{\~\~}}}{\f5\fs18\hyphpar0\qj}{{\